DateDialog - Class in gui
Dialog window that lets the user apply a filter to a table, basing on a start date and an end date.
DateDialog(String, JTable) - Constructor for class gui.DateDialog
Builds a non modal dialog window with a title and the table to filter
DateRowFilter<M,I> - Class in gui
Filter that extends a RowFilter, it is used to filter a table to let see only the values with a date between the minimum and the maximum
DateRowFilter(Date, Date) - Constructor for class gui.DateRowFilter
Costructor of the filter, sets minimum and maximum date
